# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:589
msgid ""
"**Bottom Center** – The bottom edge of the clip aligns with the bottom edge "
"of the screen; the clip is horizontally centered on the screen."
msgstr ""
"**Dolny Środek** – Dolna krawędź klipu wyrównana jest do dolnej krawędzi "
